resources.string: I didn\'t fail. I just found 10,000 ways that don\'t work.
Your problem is not the problem. Your reaction is the problem.
Real difficulties can be overcome; only imaginary ones are insurmountable.
Failure is the spice that gives success its flavor.
One cannot believe that it is possible to be happy by seeking out other people\'s unhappiness.
All progress occurs outside the comfort zone.
The capable being lives close to the need.
